data.title: What would happen if the White Fang was still alive, how would it affect the story?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 2): Sakumo Hatake, The White Fang of the Leaf, was truly a powerful shinobi that was said to rival that of even the Sannin. He struck fear in his enemies just by seeing him or hearing his name.
